Malta Fight Co. - Payment Automation System Proposal
Updated Based on Demo Feedback

Project Overview
Development of a Python-based desktop application to automate monthly payment calculations for Malta Fight Co.'s combat sports gym, integrating GoTeamUp attendance data with payment rules and generating automated reports.

Key Changes Based on Demo Feedback

1. Dashboard Enhancements ✅
• Split total attendances into Group Classes vs Private Sessions
• Display separate metrics for each category
• Real-time calculation updates

2. Rule Management System Updates ✅
• Global percentage settings for default payment splits
• Individual package customization with toggle for fixed rate vs percentage
• Price per session calculation with configurable formulas (4.3 weeks per month for 2x/week)
• Support for unlimited plans with fixed pricing
• Remove tax exempt field (not needed as tax is handled separately)

3. Payment Calculator Enhancements ✅
• Separate tracking for Group Classes vs Private Sessions per coach
• Monthly summary breakdown showing totals for each category
• Detailed transaction tracking for verification purposes
• Exception handling for discounts and special cases

4. Exception Handling System ✅
• 100% discount identification (Freedom Pass, MindBody Switch) - ignore completely
• Partial discount handling (apply percentages to discounted amount)
• Discount identification by memo containing "discount" keyword
• Legacy discount handling (Summer School, Loyalty Scheme, Fortnight Special)
• Manual override capability for unrecognized packages (like "warrior flow" class names)

Technical Specifications

Data Processing
• Import GoTeamUp attendance exports
• Import historical payment data
• Match attendance with correct membership packages
• Handle multiple profiles per customer
• Track package usage and expiration

Payment Calculations
• Group class revenue distribution (Coach/BGM/Management percentages)
• Private session revenue (80/15 split Coach/Landlord)
• Fixed rate calculations for unlimited plans
• Discount application logic
• Multi-pack session splitting

Exception Handling
• 100% discount identification and exclusion
• Partial discount percentage application
• Legacy package handling
• Manual override system for unrecognized entries

Development Phases

Phase 1: Core System (44 hours)
1. Enhanced User Interface (8 hours)
   • Updated dashboard with group/private split
   • Improved rule manager with global settings
   • Enhanced payment calculator with detailed breakdowns
   • Exception handling interface

2. Data Processing Engine (12 hours)
   • GoTeamUp attendance data import
   • Historical payment data integration
   • Package matching and validation
   • Discount identification and handling
   • Exception flagging system

3. Payment Calculation Logic (10 hours)
   • Group class revenue calculations
   • Private session revenue calculations
   • Coach payment calculations with breakdowns
   • BGM and management payment calculations
   • Discount application logic

4. Reporting Module (8 hours)
   • Monthly summary report generation
   • Coach payslip generation with detailed breakdowns
   • BGM payment reports
   • Management payment reports
   • Export functionality

5. Testing & Documentation (6 hours)
   • Comprehensive testing with sample data
   • User documentation and guides
   • Installation instructions
   • 30 days post-delivery support

